## Eduly — Per-frontend production env files.
## Copy each block into the matching app folder as `.env.production`
## BEFORE running `npm run build`. Vite inlines env vars at build time.

# ─── src/.env.production  (main admin → eduly.uz) ──────────────
VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://api.eduly.uz/api
GEMINI_API_KEY=

# ─── super-admin/.env.production  (→ super.eduly.uz) ───────────
VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://api.eduly.uz/api
GEMINI_API_KEY=

# ─── edusaas-teacher-dashboard/.env.production  (→ teacher.eduly.uz) ─
VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://api.eduly.uz/api
GEMINI_API_KEY=
